## 🤝 Contributing

StartFast is built by developers who got tired of recreating the same project structure.

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Incognitol07/startfast.git
cd startfast
pip install -e ".[dev]"
```

Found a better way to structure something? **PRs welcome!**

